# Walkthrough: M1/M2 Classifier Integration

## Overview

Integrated two trained YOLOv8n-cls models into the RapidAid pipeline:
- **M1** (`accident_classifier.pt`) — Scene-level accident classifier
- **M2** (`damage_classifier.pt`) — Per-vehicle damage detector

Both models were already wired into the pipeline with graceful degradation. This work **tightened the ensemble fusion**, added **new detection paths**, and **enhanced reporting/visualization**.

